==中微子震盪==
===内容===
2012日3月8日，大亞灣中微子實驗國際合作組宣佈<ref>{{cite journal|title=Observation of electron-antineutrino disappearance at Daya Bay |url=http://resolver.caltech.edu/CaltechAUTHORS:20120521-073412262 |author=Daya Bay Collaboration |year=2012 |journal=Physical Review Letters |volume=108 |issue=17 |page=171803 |doi=10.1103/PhysRevLett.108.171803 |arxiv=1203.1669 |bibcode=2012PhRvL.108q1803A}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Adrian Cho |url=http://news.sciencemag.org/sciencenow/2012/03/physicists-in-china-nail-a-key.html |title=Physicists in China Nail a Key Neutrino Measurement |date=8 March 2012 |publisher=ScienceNow |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509234721/http://news.sciencemag.org/sciencenow/2012/03/physicists-in-china-nail-a-key.html |archivedate=2013年5月9日 |access-date=2012年3月18日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Eugenie Samuel Reich |url=http://www.nature.com/news/neutrino-oscillations-measured-with-record-precision-1.10202 |title=Neutrino oscillations measured with record precision |date=8 March 2012 |publisher=NatureNews |doi=10.1038/nature.2012.10202 |access-date=2012-03-18 |archive-date=2012-10-06 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BDqIbMwa?url=http://www.nature.com/news/neutrino-oscillations-measured-with-record-precision-1.10202 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，發現一種新的[[中微子震盪|中微子震盪]]，其震盪機率為<math>\sin^2 (2\theta_{13})=0.092\pm 0.017 </math>。

在2015年Moriond物理学会议上，新的最适合的混合角和质量差被提出：<ref>{{Cite journal|url = http://arxiv.org/abs/1505.03641|title = Recent Results from Daya Bay Reactor Neutrino Experiment|last = |first = |date = 14 May 2015|journal = arXiv:1505.03641|doi = |pmid = |access-date = |archive-date = 2019-12-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191224193901/https://arxiv.org/abs/1505.03641|dead-url = no}}</ref>

<math>\sin^2(2\theta_{13}) = 0.084 \pm 0.005, \quad |\Delta m^2_{ee}| = 2.44^{+10}_{-11} \times 10^{-3} {\rm eV}^2</math>

===意义===
假若這結果成立，物理學者可以開始研究[[中微子|中微子]]與[[反中微子|反中微子]]之間的[[不對稱性|不對稱性]]，從而嘗試解釋為甚麼宇宙中的物質超多於反物質<ref>{{cite web| title =大亚湾中微子实验发现新的中微子振荡| publisher =中国科学院高能物理研究所| date =03-08-2012| url =http://www.ihep.cas.cn/xwdt/gnxw/201203/t20120308_3450968.html| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20120312053258/http://www.ihep.cas.cn/xwdt/gnxw/201203/t20120308_3450968.html| archivedate =2012-03-12| access-date =2012-03-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nature.com/news/neutrino-oscillations-measured-with-record-precision-1.10202 |title=Neutrino oscillations measured with record precision |publisher=nature |date=2012-03-08 |accessdate=2012-03-18 |archive-date=2012-10-06 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BDqIbMwa?url=http://www.nature.com/news/neutrino-oscillations-measured-with-record-precision-1.10202 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。大亚湾的研究员通过此次得出的精确值击败了同时参与此项目的另外四个竞争团队，它们分别是[[日本|日本]]的[[T2K實驗|T2K實驗]]、[[美国|美国]][[费米实验室|费米实验室]]的{{le|主注入器中微子震盪探索|MINOS}}、[[法国|法国]]的{{le|雙紹斯實驗|Double Chooz}}以及[[韩国|韩国]]的{{le|中微子震盪反應堆實驗|Reactor Experiment for Neutrino Oscillation}}<ref name=sc>{{cite news |url=http://news.sciencemag.org/sciencenow/2012/03/physicists-in-china-nail-a-key.html |title=Physicists in China Nail a Key Neutrino Measurement |publisher=Science |date=2012-03-08 |accessdate=2012-03-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509234721/http://news.sciencemag.org/sciencenow/2012/03/physicists-in-china-nail-a-key.html |archivedate=2013-05-09 }}</ref>。

參與者邢志忠自評「不是诺贝尔奖量级，但很重要」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://special.caixin.com/2012-03-09/100366425.html |title=大亚湾突破，够不够诺贝尔奖_特色频道_财新网 |access-date=2015-05-03 |archive-date=2020-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200216215845/http://special.caixin.com/2012-03-09/100366425.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

